# Activities
### Nabisco Activities (30+)
# Each activity will be linked to a customer or opportunity, with unique subject, type, dueAt, description, status, and distributor
POST {{baseUrl}}/activities
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subject": "Oreo Product Launch Call",
  "type": "call",
  "dueAt": "2026-03-20T14:00:00Z",
  "description": "Kickoff call for Oreo expansion",
  "relatedType": "customer",
  "relatedId": 1,
  "status": "scheduled",
  "customFields": { "distributor": "Sysco" }
}

